Summary: This happened over my home over an hours duration
divs: Sighting DetailsThis was late evening when friends and I were outside and started noticing lots of objects in the sky, one of them was thought to be a helicopter, and after turning off the camera, we saw one behind us, and what I recorded was not a helicopter, as for the photo, I was trying to take a pic instead and I thought I got nothing until I watched on my computer, I noticed that either it was a flying tether, or the object was moving so fast that I got it in 1 frame, there is no blur in or around the photo.
